$f=-3x_{1}^2+6x_{1}x_{3}-3x_{3}^2\\
A=\left|\begin{array}{cc}
-3 & 3\\
3 & -3\end{array}\right|\\

\left|\begin{array}{cc}
-3-\lambda & 3\\
3 & -3-\lambda\end{array}\right|=0;\quad \lambda^2+6\lambda=0;\\
\lambda_{1}=0\\
\lambda_{2}=-6

\lambda_{1}=0:\\
\left(\begin{array}{cc}
-3 & 3\\
0 & 0\end{array}\right) \Rightarrow -x_{1}+x_{3}=0\\
\begin{cases}
x_{1}=x_{3}\\
x_{3}=x_{3}\end{cases} \Rightarrow \vec a_{1}=(1,1)\\
\lambda_{2}=-6:\\
\left(\begin{array}{cc}
3 & 3\\
3 & 3\end{array}\right) \Rightarrow \begin{cases}
x_{1}=-x_{3}\\
x_{3}=x_{3}\end{cases} \Rightarrow \vec a_{2} = (-1, 1)\\ 

|\vec a_{1}|=\sqrt{2}\\
|\vec a_{2}|=\sqrt{2}\\
\vec a_{1} \cdot \vec a_{2}= -1 + 1 = 0; \Rightarrow \vec a_{1} \perp \vec a_{2}\\
Нормирование:
\vec a_{1}=(\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}, \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}})\\
\vec a_{2}=(-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}, \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}})\\
Матрица преобразования:
P=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}& -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\\
\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\end{array}\right)\\
f(y_{1},y_{2})=0 \cdot y_{1}^2-6y_{2}^2
$
